  <Docs>
    <summary>Defines identifiers used to indicate the direction of parameter and argument declarations.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[

## Remarks
 <xref:System.CodeDom.FieldDirection> allows for passing arguments to functions by reference, or using incoming or outgoing parameters.



